    <description>An open source and free screen pixel ruler written in C# that is a clone of MioPlanet PixelRuler.

# Features

* Vertical and hortizontal rotatable ruler.
* Flip ruler markings to the opposite side of the ruler.
* Shift the start of the ruler to your cursor location when using `Ctrl + Shift + Alt + S`.
* Support themes to customize your experience.
* Global hotkeys for operating the ruler.
* Guidelines to lock your mouse cursor hortizontally or vertically.
